intent.user_query: What is the trend of total sales amount over each quarter of 2023?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT EXTRACT(QUARTER FROM SaleDate) AS SaleQuarter, SUM(TotalAmount) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM SaleDate) = 2023 GROUP BY SaleQuarter ORDER BY SaleQuarter;

arguments.sql: SELECT EXTRACT(QUARTER FROM SaleDate) AS SaleQuarter, SUM(TotalAmount) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM SaleDate) = 2023 GROUP BY SaleQuarter ORDER BY SaleQuarter;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
